creator: OurGroceries, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
OurGroceries automatically keeps your family’s grocery list in sync with the latest changes—on every family member’s phone or web browser.

Every change to your shared shopping list is visible in seconds. See items being checked off as your partner shops!

• Share your shopping lists with family members, even if they have an iPhone.
• Share your recipes too; add them to your shopping list with one tap.
• Add items using your Amazon Alexa device, such as the Echo.
• Add items using your Google Assistant device, such as the Google Home.
• Convenient shopping with your Android Wear watch.
• Add photos to items (premium version only).
• Add items by scanning barcodes (premium version only).
• Ad-supported, but upgradable to turn off the ads.
• iPhone and web versions are also available.

descriptionShort: The easiest way to share your family’s grocery shopping—and it’s FREE!

title: Our Groceries Shopping List

creator: OurGroceries, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Never forget your list at home, and always know the exact right items to get. Add milk to the grocery list and your partner sees it immediately—even if they’re already shopping at the store!

"I love technology, but I also love simplicity. I've found the best of both in OurGroceries." —The Kitchn (https://www.thekitchn.com/ourgroceries-a-grocery-list-app-that-simply-works-165395)

Everyone in your household can share the same grocery list, and they can add items whether they’re at home, at work, or on the go, using OurGroceries with their smartphone, tablet, laptop, or even Alexa.

At the grocery store, the OurGroceries app makes your shopping easy, efficient, and stress free. An organized list lets you visit only the aisles needed for each trip, and adding photos makes sure the right items always come home—regardless of who’s doing the shopping.

Download the OurGroceries app and simplify your grocery shopping today!

All features are available in the free ad-supported version, and with a single low-cost upgrade your whole family goes ad-free.

FEATURES:
• Share the same grocery list with all family members.
• Make sure your partner gets exactly the right brand or size by adding a photo or note to any grocery list item.
• Every change to your shared shopping list is visible in seconds. See items being checked off as your partner shops!
• Make shopping faster and easier by organizing your shopping list by category or aisle.
• Organize your grocery items automatically using the built-in category suggestions.
• Browse your favorite meal ideas anytime by cataloging your recipes in OurGroceries.
• Add a recipe’s ingredients to your shopping list with one tap.
• Available for Android, iPhone, and iPad, and can be used from any laptop.
• Use Alexa, Siri, or Google Assistant to add items with voice commands.
• Use your Apple Watch or Android Wear watch for convenient hands-free shopping.
• Create as many separate shopping lists as you wish, or keep it simple and use just one.
• All your items, lists, and recipes are automatically backed up by OurGroceries. Upgrade, replace, or restore your phone without worrying about losing your data.
• You can scan a barcode to add an item to your grocery list.
• Also great for non-grocery lists like errands, reminders, movies, and gifts!

Visit https://www.ourgroceries.com for more information.
descriptionShort: The easiest app to share your family grocery list and simplify grocery shopping!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
• New way to add items using the + button in the lower-right.
• Can search for shopping lists and recipes.
• Can make shortcuts for directly scanning barcodes or adding items by voice.

"I love technology, but I also love simplicity. I've found the best of both in OurGroceries." —The Kitchn (https://www.thekitchn.com/ourgroceries-a-grocery-list-app-that-simply-works-165395)

Everyone in your household can share the same grocery list, and they can add items whether they’re at home, at work, or on the go, using OurGroceries with their smartphone, tablet, laptop, or even Alexa.

At the grocery store, the OurGroceries app makes your shopping easy, efficient, and stress free. An organized list lets you visit only the aisles needed for each trip, and adding photos makes sure the right items always come home—regardless of who’s doing the shopping.

Download the OurGroceries app and simplify your grocery shopping today!

All features are available in the free ad-supported version, and with a single low-cost upgrade your whole family goes ad-free.

FEATURES:
• Share the same grocery list with all family members.
• Make sure your partner gets exactly the right brand or size by adding a photo or note to any grocery list item.
• Every change to your shared shopping list is visible in seconds. See items being checked off as your partner shops!
• Make shopping faster and easier by organizing your shopping list by category or aisle.
• Organize your grocery items automatically using the built-in category suggestions, including region-specific suggestions for Canada, UK, Ireland, Australia, New Zealand (NZ), South Africa (SA), and more.
• Browse your favorite meal ideas anytime by cataloging your recipes in OurGroceries.
• Add a recipe’s ingredients to your shopping list with one tap.
• Available for Android, iPhone, and iPad, and can be used from any laptop.
• Use Alexa, Siri, or Google Assistant to add items with voice commands.
• Use your Apple Watch or Wear OS watch for convenient hands-free shopping.
• Create as many separate shopping lists as you wish, or keep it simple and use just one.
• All your items, lists, and recipes are automatically backed up by OurGroceries. Upgrade, replace, or restore your phone without worrying about losing your data.
• You can scan a barcode to add an item to your grocery list.
• Also great for non-grocery lists like errands, reminders, movies, and gifts!

Visit https://www.ourgroceries.com for more information.
descriptionShort: The easiest app to share your family grocery list and simplify grocery shopping!
